OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777892572
OL,3,CWoman in 50s stabbed in daylight park
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FDetectives are investigating after a
OL,7,Fwoman was stabbed in a park in
OL,8,FStockton.
OL,10,FCleveland Police said the incident,
OL,11,Fbelieved to have been targeted,
OL,12,Fhappened in Hardwick Green Park at
OL,13,Fabout 1:40pm on Sunday (3 May).
OL,15,FThe force said a woman in her 50s was
OL,16,Fapproached by a male who was described
OL,17,Fas wearing dark clothing and a face
OL,18,Fcovering. A second man is also
OL,19,Fbelieved to have been present on a
OL,20,Fpedal bike.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
