PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777892572
OL,3,CWoman in 50s stabbed in daylight park
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FThe man is reported to have attacked
OL,7,Fthe woman with a knife before both
OL,8,Fmales made off into the wooded area.
OL,10,FThe woman suffered a stab wound which
OL,11,Fis not believed to be life-threatening.
OL,13,FDetective Sergeant Paul Edmonds, from
OL,14,FStockton CID, said: "I understand this
OL,15,Fincident may cause some concern,
OL,16,Fhowever, this appears to have been a
OL,17,Ftargeted assault with no threat to the
OL,18,Fwider community.
OL,26,@vD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
