FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777892572
OL,3,CWoman in 50s stabbed in daylight park
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,F"Detectives are carrying out several
OL,7,Flines of enquiries and are urging
OL,8,Fanyone who was in the park at the time
OL,9,Fand saw what happened to contact the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,F"Similarly, we'd like to hear from
OL,13,Fanyone with any relevant dash cam or
OL,14,FCCTV footage."
OL,16,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,17,Fcall 101 quoting reference 083578.
OL,18,FInformation can also be passed to
OL,19,FCrimestoppers anonymously online or by
OL,20,Fcalling 0800 555 111.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
